name: Supermodel Star - Fashion Game
description:
It’s your chance to rule the runway! Style the hottest supermodel around and get her ready to strut the catwalk! Shop at the trendiest boutiques, dress up in the most stylish fashion outfits, and prep your model for the most anticipated fashion show of the year! Don’t forget to match your supermodel’s style to the fashion show!

√ Style your supermodel with ultimate fashion look!
√ Experience the glamorous world of modeling, style and the runway!
√ Makeup & Dress up your model in the trendiest star styles!
√ Choose from tons of Makeup: eye shadows, lipsticks and more!
√ Walk the runway like a pro supermodel star! (Don’t fall in those high heels!)
√ Relax at the spa and enjoy the most amazing face and body creams!
√ Strike a star pose! Experience your supermodel’s big-time fashion magazine cover shoot!
